&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain CAD modeling algorithms (editing brep data structures, developing topological algorithms, etc)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
